                        Resurrection. Whoever helps ease one in difficulty, Allah will make it easy for him in this
                        world and in the Hereafter. (Sahih Muslim). Donate generously to help our brothers and sisters
                        in Palestine today.</p>
                    <a href="" class="mt-4 text-small">Manage your donation</a>
